name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.client.key.provider.cache.expiry
description: DFS client security key cache expiration in milliseconds.

name: httpfs.buffer.size
description: The size buffer to be used when creating or opening httpfs filesystem IO stream.

name: ftp.bytes-per-checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  ftp.stream-buffer-size

name: dfs.ha.fencing.ssh.connect-timeout
description:
SSH connection timeout, in milliseconds, to use with the builtin
    sshfence fencer.

name: dfs.ha.zkfc.port
description:
The port number that the zookeeper failover controller RPC
    server binds to.
